							<h5><a href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/12/04/will-california-ever-let-sierra-nevada-forests-burn/" title="Read: Will California Ever Let Sierra Nevada Forests Burn?">Will California Ever Let Sierra Nevada Forests Burn?</a>
			<span class="postMetaHeaderCommentCount commentCount hidden">
					<i class="icon"></i>
					<a class="commentCountLink commentCountNumberOnly commentCountNoPrompt" href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/12/04/will-california-ever-let-sierra-nevada-forests-burn/"></a>
				</span>			</h5>
			<p class="summary">
			In the Sierra Nevada, California&#8217;s main forest fire problem lies in not letting forests burn.<a href="//dotearth.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/12/04/will-california-ever-let-sierra-nevada-forests-burn/" class="more-link">Read&#160;more&#8230;</a></p>
